node.text: Well that was a crazy race. Haiden started with a far outside gate pick got going crashed on the first lap. Got back up put on a good charge from behind which was fun to watch got into a little battle with @krystian.janik_27 And after he passed him he missed his shift lost drive tried to get out of the way and guessed wrong on where Janik was going . He thought Janik would stay outside following the outside line he was in as u can see him look left for him. Simple mistake and racing things happen really fast. Janik is a buddy. Purely a racing incident. Must say the announcers got it wrong Way wrong. But that happens. We’re all human.  Main thing is haiden is not seriously Injured . Bumped and and bruised but not giving up ! Thx to everyone who checked on haiden and have our back.💪🏼 #Racing #moto is #gnarly @octaneco

node.text: Good start to the week. 1st moto is always the one to shake off the nerves and dust.  Stoked to see haiden rip a holeshot he has been working on starts a lot. We missed the bike set up a tad but haiden adapted to it finding good lines.. He was happy with the win but not content . We should get better each gate drop that’s always the fun part and the goal of racing .  Haiden is enjoying the last rides on a mini bike.  Thx to the fans that traveled to come watch. One moto tomorrow at 12p central time @racertv .com  thx for watching and supporting the moto industry. #race #moto @racerxonline All vids will be up on our YouTube “The Deegans “
